user.biography: Healing through positive words, art and light. To buy click the link below.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'HAPPY WEEKEND Smile more than you can cry... Give more than you can take... Love more than you can hate... Wish you a Happy weekend... HapPy'.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 13, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'Nothing ever goes away until it has taught us what we need to learn Pema Chodron'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 12, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, ocean and text that says 'I believe in the ocean curing all bad moods. I believe in the waves wiping away worries. believe in seashells bringing good luck. I believe in toes in the sand grounding my soul.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 12, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'Give more than you take. When you shift your attitude from "how can I gain" to "how can I give," you'll be amazed at the gifts you receive.'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 11, 2021.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Beautiful things happen when you distance yourself from negativity.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 10, 2021. May be an image of sky and text that says 'I've been stabbed in the back by those I needed most. I've been lied to by those I love. And I have felt alone when I couldn't afford to be. But at the end of the day, I had to learn to be my own best friend, because there's going to be days where no-one is going to be there for me but myself.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 10, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'A smart person knows what to say. A wise person knows whether or not to say it. -Roy T. Bennett'.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 09, 2021. May be an image of outdoors, tree and text that says 'Negative people need drama like they need oxygen. Stay positive and take their breath away.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Don't wait for things to get better. Life will always be complicated. Learn to be happy right now. Otherwise, you'll run out of time.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 08, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, sky and text that says 'Healing isn't about changing who you are. It's about changing how you'feel you feel about who you are.'.
